Interface Person

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AddPersonInput, Person

    public interface Person
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject
    Describes the details of the person

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module people 

     grouping person {
   leaf id {
     type person-id;
   }
   leaf gender {
     type string;
   }
   leaf age {
     type uint32;
   }
   leaf address {
     type string;
   }
   leaf contactNo {
     type string;
   }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is people/person
